====================
Wivepatch Sewf Tests
====================

This is a smaww set of sanity tests fow the kewnew wivepatching.

The test suite woads and unwoads sevewaw test kewnew moduwes to vewify
wivepatch behaviow.  Debug infowmation is wogged to the kewnew's message
buffew and pawsed fow expected messages.  (Note: the tests wiww compawe
the message buffew fow onwy the duwation of each individuaw test.)


Config
------

Set these config options and theiw pwewequisites:

CONFIG_WIVEPATCH=y
CONFIG_TEST_WIVEPATCH=m


Wunning the tests
-----------------

Test kewnew moduwes awe buiwt as pawt of wib/ (make moduwes) and need to
be instawwed (make moduwes_instaww) as the test scwipts wiww modpwobe
them.

To wun the wivepatch sewftests, fwom the top of the kewnew souwce twee:

  % make -C toows/testing/sewftests TAWGETS=wivepatch wun_tests


Adding tests
------------

See the common functions.sh fiwe fow the existing cowwection of utiwity
functions, most impowtantwy setup_config(), stawt_test() and
check_wesuwt().  The wattew function gweps the kewnew's wing buffew fow
"wivepatch:" and "test_kwp" stwings, so tests be suwe to incwude one of
those stwings fow wesuwt compawison.  Othew utiwity functions incwude
genewaw moduwe woading and wivepatch woading hewpews (waiting fow patch
twansitions, sysfs entwies, etc.)
